<p><span style="font-size:1.2em;"><br />
The individual known only as “Number 27” that hosts the mysterious “Station Number 27” has finally broken their tradition of one-way communication through their broadcasts.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:1.2em;">The individual has rapidly become an important part of many friends and family since its initial discovery by Frederick J. Canine, a corporeal whom has been central in the ongoing story of the station, deciphering the cryptic broadcasts of Station Number 27.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:1.2em;">The station is well-known for acting in a manner comparable to terran numbers stations in which encrypted messages are sent to specific, anonymous listeners who decode the messages. If conducted correctly, these messages are impossible to be decrypted by unintended listeners.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:1.2em;">Despite all former attempts at communication being ignored by Number 27, the individual has finally joined with the sub-collective devoted to it, “Station#27”.</span></p>
